{"text": "Comisaría ko távagua oikuaauka oñemondahague Miguel ra'anga ha ocho espadines de oro, bronce ha plata pe Oratorio San Miguelgui.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9997098445892334, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 19, "num_words_punct_spacy": 21, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 19, "num_chars": 128, "bad_word_counts": {"mondaha": 1}}
{"text": "Anive reñembotavy ndejupe, nde ha’e opa mba’e ypy, ndepypentevoi heñói umi ne rembipota, ne mba’embyasy, nde py’amirî", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9999030828475952, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 17, "num_words_punct_spacy": 21, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 17, "num_chars": 117, "bad_word_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Ko'ã manifestante ombyasy hikuái ko'ã mitãmimi opyta merienda escolar ÿre, oreka consecuencia, he'i hikuái, umi senador mondaha ha'eháicha Jorge Oviedo Matto, ojerúre hikuái torrenunsia \"por las buenas\".", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9996814727783203, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 27, "num_words_punct_spacy": 34, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 27, "num_chars": 203, "bad_word_counts": {"mondaha": 1}}
{"text": "Pero, iñambuéva ko'ã escasa dignidad senador-kuéra, peteî valiente ha perseverante grupo oinupãva hera aryma conciencia: umi escrachadores, tavyagua omomýiva.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9999189376831055, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 19, "num_words_punct_spacy": 26, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 20, "num_chars": 158, "bad_word_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Ohai avei ñoha’anga ombohéra “Nderasóre”.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 1.0000088214874268, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 5, "num_words_punct_spacy": 8, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 5, "num_chars": 41, "bad_word_counts": {"nderasóre": 1}}
{"text": "Pe “ñembotavy” peteî deporte jepiguáichaite oñeha'ãva político-kuéra ojoapytépe osêvo hi'ári, taha'e ha'eháicha, peteî problema urticante, oheka mboyve solución ou porãvéva.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9997617602348328, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 20, "num_words_punct_spacy": 28, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 21, "num_chars": 173, "bad_word_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Upéicha avei, ára 29 jasypakôi ary 2009-pe, tetâ ruvicha Fernando Lugo omboajékuri Ñe’ênguéra Léi, ombojojáva Guarani ha Castellano puru taha’e ha’ehápe; jepémo upéicha, ary 2009 guive MEC omboykesékuri Guarani ñe’ême mbo’esyry mbohapyhágui, mitârusukuéra rekombo’égui; ja’eporâsérô, MEC o’apo’i leikuéra ha avei oñembotavy umi 87% ñane retâyguágui oipurúva Guarani ñe’ê hekohápe; ha amo ipahápe, ary 2013-pe MEC omboykékuri Guarani ñe'ême upe mbo'esyrýgui.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.999823272228241, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 60, "num_words_punct_spacy": 72, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 60, "num_chars": 457, "bad_word_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Pápa he'i tekotevêha “ñamoingovejey umi tekopyjegua ha jehupytyrâ tuichavéva itapykuejepéva oîvégui hekojejapóva (ivýro ha ijejapóva)”.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.99211585521698, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 15, "num_words_punct_spacy": 20, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 15, "num_chars": 135, "bad_word_counts": {"výro": 1}}
{"text": "– Anína reñembotavy reína Kirikiri.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9999717473983765, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 5, "num_words_punct_spacy": 6, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 4, "num_chars": 35, "bad_word_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Tavy ha mba'epota poguýpe.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 1.0000097751617432, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 4, "num_words_punct_spacy": 5, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 4, "num_chars": 26, "bad_word_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Profesional omohenda pe sala de endoscopia centro asistencial peteî  cartel he'íva “oñesuspende estudio endoscópico-kuéra itajasúgui, tavy ha ndovaléigui autoridades” péva ikatu haguã omoñe'ê usuariokuéra avei autoridades competentes.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9998377561569214, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 27, "num_words_punct_spacy": 34, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 29, "num_chars": 234, "bad_word_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Ikatúrô rejejuhu po’a ha po’a’ŷ ndive ha reñangarekojajárô umi mokôi teko mbotavyhárare;", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9978247880935669, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 12, "num_words_punct_spacy": 13, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 12, "num_chars": 88, "bad_word_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Heta ára ohasa rire, peteî pyhare, Anai ombotavy hese oñangarekóvape ha osêkuri oñani.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9789943099021912, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 13, "num_words_punct_spacy": 16, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 13, "num_chars": 86, "bad_word_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Ko'ã manifestante ombyasy hikuái ko'ã mitãmimi opyta merienda escolar ÿre, oreka consecuencia, he'i hikuái, umi senador mondaha ha'eháicha Jorge Oviedo Matto, ojerúre hikuái torrenunsia \"por las buenas\".", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9996814727783203, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 27, "num_words_punct_spacy": 34, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 27, "num_chars": 203, "bad_word_counts": {"mondaha": 1}}
{"text": "Ani ndepy’arô nendivevoi, ha ani rembohasa ambue akâ ári mba’e ndéve ojehúva, ejehechakuaa ko’áĝa ỹramo reñembotavýta ku mitâ oñembotavyháicha ijupe.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.999212920665741, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 20, "num_words_punct_spacy": 23, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 20, "num_chars": 149, "bad_word_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Tavy ha mba'epota poguýpe.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 1.0000097751617432, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 4, "num_words_punct_spacy": 5, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 4, "num_chars": 26, "bad_word_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Roñemanifesta ohapejokóvo, ningún vehículo ojehapejoko, upéi he'i gua'u umi vecino ore supuestamente romonda ha upévare romondaha chupekuéra.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.999769389629364, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 17, "num_words_punct_spacy": 20, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 17, "num_chars": 141, "bad_word_counts": {"mondaha": 1}}
{"text": "¿Peikuaápa mba’e oiko peteî jagua ha peteî jaguakuña ojojuhu jave tapépe?", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9997285008430481, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 11, "num_words_punct_spacy": 13, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 11, "num_chars": 73, "bad_word_counts": {"jaguakuña": 1}}
{"text": "Ñande Pápa ndohechaporâi “ñemboyke ojapóva umi ipoguasúva” ha “ñembotavy reko ambuekuéra oñandukáva” tekoháre.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9999768733978271, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 13, "num_words_punct_spacy": 18, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 13, "num_chars": 110, "bad_word_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Omomba'e guasu oñembokatupyrývo Japón oho hikuái fábrica de procesamiento de sésamo ha soja upéicha ombohetáve sistema tetãme, omokyre'ÿ microempresa omba'apóva cooperativaícha.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9992796778678894, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 21, "num_words_punct_spacy": 23, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 21, "num_chars": 177, "bad_word_counts": {"vaícha": 1}}
{"text": "Jepopete guasu –mención especial abogada María Esther Roa ha iñirûnguérape– omboykéva hembiapo ha ojapo ko'ã mba'e umi mondaha público ha ambue impresentable-kuéra ndikatuvéiva ojapo  impunemente fechoría-kuéra ojapóva.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9988885521888733, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 27, "num_words_punct_spacy": 35, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 30, "num_chars": 219, "bad_word_counts": {"mondaha": 1}}
{"text": "Ko'ã oporombotavyva'ekue monandípe hetápe ohejáva, odenunsia Estado paraguayo-pe Comisión Interamericana de Derechos Humanos (CIDH) renondépe, opresenta mboriahu ha jeiko asýpe ojeiko hapykuéri oñeha'ãvo opa sindicalismo.", "corpus": "americasnlp2023", "corpus_file": "guarani-spanish_train.gn", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9993646740913391, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 25, "num_words_punct_spacy": 32, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 26, "num_chars": 221, "bad_word_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
